data.description: Set on almost 3 acres of land, this property is awaiting your improvements and personal touches. This well-built home offers tons of finished square feet and even more of an upside potential. With 3 bedrooms on the main level, a finished basement, 2 bathrooms, a family room overlooking the fenced side-yard, a 2,700 square foot pole barn, and backing up to The Burl Oaks Golf Club, this property is a MUST SEE. Whether someone is looking to tear this home down and build new, or improve upon the existing home and build equity, this property has options. Rarely do opportunities like this come around. Plan you tour of this new listing today and get ready to call this house, your new home.
